			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>This song lowers you on the mob's hate list but will never completely remove you.  In other words, if you are soloing and you want to lose agro, this song is of no use whatsoever.  If you have others with you, it will be possible to lower your position on the hate list enough that the other members of your group get agro.  But if your intention is to camp out while they have the agro, bear in mind that sitting down adds a TON of agro to your position on the list.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
